      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――八月三日　朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――八月三日　朝",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 366.66651959999984,
          "startTime": 1.1666665196
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよ～ちょっと寝坊しちゃった\nみんなもうお仕事に出たのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "おはよ～ちょっと寝坊しちゃった\nみんなもうお仕事に出たのかな？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6666664878,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.999999999998,
          "startTime": 16.7666664878
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、おはよう渚。お互い仕事に行く前に会えて\n良かったわ。はいこれ。お誕生日おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ、おはよう渚。お互い仕事に行く前に会えて\n良かったわ。はいこれ。お誕生日おめでとう",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5333331544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "わっ怜ちゃん！　ありがとう！　プレゼントまで\n用意してくれたんだね！　見てもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "わっ怜ちゃん！　ありがとう！　プレゼントまで\n用意してくれたんだね！　見てもいい？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6666668136,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666699999,
          "startTime": 30.8333334803
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "なんだろう？　本みたいだけど……はっ！　これって\nもしかして、盆募盆先生の新刊『恋の暑中見舞い』！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "なんだろう？　本みたいだけど……はっ！　これって\nもしかして、盆募盆先生の新刊『恋の暑中見舞い』！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2333334803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、こないだラジオで好きだって話してたでしょ？\n今日発売だったし朝渡そうと思って本屋さんに寄ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "うん、こないだラジオで好きだって話してたでしょ？\n今日発売だったし朝渡そうと思って本屋さんに寄ったの",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1465913886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん嬉しいよ～何より怜ちゃんが\n私のラジオを聞いててくれたのが嬉しい！　感激！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "怜ちゃん嬉しいよ～何より怜ちゃんが\n私のラジオを聞いててくれたのが嬉しい！　感激！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0666668136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、渚大げさよ。それでそれどんな内容なの？\n私、知らずに買っちゃったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ちょっと、渚大げさよ。それでそれどんな内容なの？\n私、知らずに買っちゃったんだけど",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6999988754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "え～それ聞いちゃう？　聞いちゃうの？\n聞いて驚きたまえー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "え～それ聞いちゃう？　聞いちゃうの？\n聞いて驚きたまえー！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1891076172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "もう、何よそのノリ？　起きたばかりからか少し変よ\n二人ともこの後仕事なんだから簡潔にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "もう、何よそのノリ？　起きたばかりからか少し変よ\n二人ともこの後仕事なんだから簡潔にね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333334803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "……それでね俳優の女の子が自分自身を武器に芸能界の\n悪い大人を手玉に取ってサバイブしていくんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……それでね俳優の女の子が自分自身を武器に芸能界の\n悪い大人を手玉に取ってサバイブしていくんだって！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1333344976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そして後半には！　唯一味方だったADの男の子と\n組んず解れつバヒーン！　ってお話なんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そして後半には！　唯一味方だったADの男の子と\n組んず解れつバヒーン！　ってお話なんだって！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6666678309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "待って興奮し過ぎ！　それよりそんな内容だったの！？\n私、特に変装せずに買っちゃったじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "待って興奮し過ぎ！　それよりそんな内容だったの！？\n私、特に変装せずに買っちゃったじゃない！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7333375493,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7933.3292642999995,
          "startTime": 119.6666668136
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでいかがわしい内容だったなんて……\n確かに帯にも淫らな言葉が並んでるみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そこまでいかがわしい内容だったなんて……\n確かに帯にも淫らな言葉が並んでるみたい……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5333344976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、終わったわ……もうSNSで『一ノ瀬怜\nいやらしい』　『一ノ瀬怜　不潔』とかあがってる頃ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はぁ、終わったわ……もうSNSで『一ノ瀬怜\nいやらしい』　『一ノ瀬怜　不潔』とかあがってる頃ね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6666668136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ～高校生の間でも話題になってる作品だし\nそういうシーンがあるからこそのリアリティだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "大丈夫だよ～高校生の間でも話題になってる作品だし\nそういうシーンがあるからこそのリアリティだから！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9333334803,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13599.999999999995,
          "startTime": 157.5333334803
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　琴乃ちゃんと待ち合わせて現場に行くんだった\nじゃあ怜ちゃん、ありがとう！　また感想伝えるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あー！　琴乃ちゃんと待ち合わせて現場に行くんだった\nじゃあ怜ちゃん、ありがとう！　また感想伝えるよ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1333100836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.9433334803
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.9433334803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、まぁ喜んでくれたし良かったのかな。早起きして\n買いに行った甲斐はあったかも。いや、でも万が一……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はあ、まぁ喜んでくれたし良かったのかな。早起きして\n買いに行った甲斐はあったかも。いや、でも万が一……",
        "id": ""
      },
